1
00:00:34,679 --> 00:00:35,320
Boss.

2
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:36,159
Where are you?

3
00:00:36,159 --> 00:00:37,920
D-Did you find Qibao?

4
00:00:38,119 --> 00:00:38,759
I'm fine.

5
00:00:39,119 --> 00:00:40,039
You didn't call the police, did you?

6
00:00:42,039 --> 00:00:43,240
I-I didn't call them.

7
00:00:43,520 --> 00:00:44,960
Did you see the kidnapper?

8
00:00:45,759 --> 00:00:46,520
He didn't show his face.

9
00:00:46,920 --> 00:00:48,240
He just made me leave 200,000.

10
00:00:48,240 --> 00:00:49,280
And told me to keep raising money.

11
00:00:50,119 --> 00:00:51,039
No, Boss, I...

12
00:00:51,039 --> 00:00:53,079
I told you, he's got to be a scammer.

13
00:00:53,280 --> 00:00:54,520
Stall him for now.

14
00:00:54,719 --> 00:00:55,479
And then...

15
00:00:55,719 --> 00:00:57,479
I'll go find Chu Feng, Qin Mo, and the others.

16
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,520
Give me an address.

17
00:00:58,520 --> 00:00:59,759
I'll bring them to find you.

18
00:01:00,119 --> 00:01:02,520
But he has Siqi's bag and hat.

19
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:04,000
I have no choice but to believe him.

20
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,040
I'll just have to put up this restaurant...

21
00:01:05,439 --> 00:01:06,159
as collateral.

22
00:01:06,159 --> 00:01:07,159
However much I can raise...

23
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,640
is what it'll have to be.

24
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:11,439
I mean, how can you fight these ruthless thugs alone?

25
00:01:11,439 --> 00:01:13,319
Listen to me, just give me an address first.

26
00:01:13,319 --> 00:01:14,719
Your safety is what matters.

27
00:01:15,079 --> 00:01:17,200
I've weathered all kinds of storms in my life.

28
00:01:17,519 --> 00:01:18,439
Don't worry about me.

29
00:01:19,879 --> 00:01:20,359
Hello?

30
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:21,640
Bos--

31
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,920
The boss has been so wise her whole life,

32
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:31,079
how can she be acting so foolish now?

33
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:32,920
She cares too much to think straight.

34
00:01:33,159 --> 00:01:34,560
She cares too much about her daughter.

35
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:35,799
She thinks money...

36
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:37,319
can save her daughter's life.

37
00:01:37,799 --> 00:01:39,920
The thing is, we don't know where Qibao is either.

38
00:01:40,319 --> 00:01:41,719
And Boss Bai is acting so impulsively.

39
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:43,400
What on earth are we going to do?

40
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:44,599
Come up with an idea, quick!

41
00:01:45,319 --> 00:01:47,680
He Siqi was kidnapped by Guo Yi.

42
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:50,200
But it's not the same group extorting Bai Ruifen.

43
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,519
This is a textbook case-within-a-case.

44
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,519
We need to sort out our priorities.

45
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:56,519
I don't care if it's a case-within-a-case.

46
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:58,439
I want to save Qibao right now.

47
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,840
Captain Chu, Sun Bo just sent word.

48
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:02,359
He found Guo Yi's address.

49
00:02:02,359 --> 00:02:03,439
It's at Nanzhuang Beili.

50
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:04,200
Come on, let's go!

51
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,040
Yu Tianfang, get out.

52
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,480
I'm not getting out even if you kill me.

53
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,000
I-I promise.

54
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,400
I-I won't interfere with your operation.

55
00:02:10,719 --> 00:02:12,240
I'll just sit in the car.

56
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:26,520
Here.

57
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,840
Your favorite buckwheat noodles.

58
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,479
Why so down?

59
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:31,479
You sick?

60
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,759
Disgusted by me?

61
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:34,280
No.

62
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:34,879
I...

63
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:37,000
I'm just... t-too hungry.

64
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,919
Can you untie me?

65
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,000
I promise.

66
00:02:42,439 --> 00:02:43,360
I won't run, I swear.

67
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,000
My wife...

68
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:02,039
used to really love the noodles I made too.

69
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:12,639
What are you smiling at?

70
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,639
I'm severely allergic to buckwheat noodles.

71
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:17,719
You killed Ma Xiaojun.

72
00:03:18,439 --> 00:03:19,840
And now you're killing me.

73
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:22,039
You'll have two lives on your hands.

74
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,639
You won't get away either.

75
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:27,080
A bite of noodles can kill you?

76
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,800
You're trying to outsmart me again.

77
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:29,960
Look.

78
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,120
First, I get a red rash.

79
00:03:32,759 --> 00:03:34,319
Then I can't breathe.

80
00:03:36,159 --> 00:03:37,599
Finally, cardiac arrest.

81
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:39,919
And then, death.

82
00:03:40,479 --> 00:03:41,039
No.

83
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:42,400
You can't die.

84
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,360
Dying would let Chen Dahui off too easy.

85
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,439
If you don't want me to die,

86
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:48,879
take me to a hospital.

87
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:50,199
No way.

88
00:03:50,879 --> 00:03:51,560
I know...

89
00:03:51,879 --> 00:03:52,680
there are anti-inflammatories.

90
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,080
I absolutely won't let you die.

91
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,199
I'll go get medicine for you.

92
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,439
I'll go buy you medicine right now.

93
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:05,960
Trying to die, huh?

94
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:08,520
I won't let you die that easily.

95
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:10,319
I'm going to torment you slowly.

96
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:42,959
This is the place.

97
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:48,519
Police! Freeze!

98
00:05:30,839 --> 00:05:31,319
Captain Chu.

99
00:06:19,519 --> 00:06:20,240
Surprised?

100
00:06:22,279 --> 00:06:24,040
If you hadn't tried to be so smart,

101
00:06:24,759 --> 00:06:26,439
I wouldn't have put you in here.

102
00:06:39,439 --> 00:06:40,399
Realize your mistake now?

103
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:43,560
Admit you were wrong,

104
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,040
and I'll go buy you medicine.

105
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,040
Even if I freeze to death,

106
00:06:47,399 --> 00:06:48,759
I will never admit I'm wrong to you.

107
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,439
Fine.

108
00:06:53,199 --> 00:06:54,000
You've got guts.

109
00:06:54,639 --> 00:06:56,279
Then enjoy yourself in here.

110
00:07:09,399 --> 00:07:10,240
I didn't see anything.

111
00:07:10,519 --> 00:07:11,519
I don't know you.

112
00:07:12,839 --> 00:07:13,279
Bro,

113
00:07:13,279 --> 00:07:14,199
please don't kill me.

114
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,040
Take whatever you want.

115
00:07:17,439 --> 00:07:18,199
It was you.

116
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,600
You deliberately ran over my wife.

117
00:07:20,959 --> 00:07:22,120
You caused her miscarriage.

118
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,560
And now she's in a vegetative state.

119
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,079
How can you make up for that?

120
00:07:25,199 --> 00:07:26,560
I don't know.

121
00:07:27,399 --> 00:07:28,519
I don't know.

122
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,639
I didn't do it on purpose.

123
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,839
I was going after her...

124
00:07:30,839 --> 00:07:32,759
I meant to hit her boyfriend.

125
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:33,600
You animal.

126
00:07:34,399 --> 00:07:35,639
She's the real culprit.

127
00:07:35,839 --> 00:07:36,920
If I had hit her,

128
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:39,360
your wife and child would be fine, right?

129
00:07:43,959 --> 00:07:45,279
I really want to kill this bastard.

130
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:47,879
But my upbringing won't let me do that.

131
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,560
So I'm giving you this chance.

132
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,079
You decide.

133
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:53,399
Whether to kill him,

134
00:07:54,279 --> 00:07:55,199
or spare him.

135
00:08:25,639 --> 00:08:28,040
Didn't you say buckwheat noodles would kill you?

136
00:08:28,439 --> 00:08:29,639
Then die!

137
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,639
That Chen Dahui

138
00:08:31,759 --> 00:08:33,840
is just a scammer.

139
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:35,120
A scammer!

140
00:08:53,279 --> 00:08:54,360
Let me finish you off.

141
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:09,480
Didn't you say it was an accident?

142
00:09:09,799 --> 00:09:11,919
I really wanted to believe it was an accident.

143
00:09:11,919 --> 00:09:13,440
But you're just scum.

144
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:15,480
How dare you bite the hand that feeds you.

145
00:09:16,399 --> 00:09:17,720
I have no choice but to kill you.

146
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,759
So you're not dead.

147
00:09:44,759 --> 00:09:46,679
You almost got me killed!

148
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:32,440
Qin Mo!

149
00:11:32,639 --> 00:11:33,279
Call for help, quick!

150
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:34,960
Requesting backup.

151
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,960
We have a fatality in the logistics freezer area.

152
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:37,480
Siqi!

153
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:38,960
We have a fatality in the logistics freezer area.

154
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,000
Siqi!

155
00:11:57,639 --> 00:11:58,519
Call an ambulance!

156
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:08,919
He Siqi!

157
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:12,440
Qibao!

158
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:21,440
Tianfang!

159
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:23,759
Tianfang!

160
00:12:30,399 --> 00:12:30,840
Siqi!

161
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:31,799
Qibao!

162
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:33,799
Hold on!

163
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,440
Let's go, get out!

164
00:12:36,519 --> 00:12:37,399
It'll be over soon.

165
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:38,320
Let's go.
